Third Department,

February, 1973

(February 16, 1973) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Edward Polhill, Petitioner, v. J. Edwin La Vallee, as Superintendent of Clinton Correctional Facility, Respondent.

Application for writ of habeas corpus pursuant .to CPLR 7002 (subd. [b], par. 2) denied as insufficient. Staley, Jr., J. P., Greeriblott, Cooke, Sweeney and Main, JJ., concur.
